@2703  = ~BLADE: The Blade is an expert fighter and adventurer whose bardic acting abilities make <PRO_HIMHER> appear more intimidating and fearsome. This Bard's fighting style is flashy and entertaining, but is also lethally dangerous.

Abilities:
- May achieve Specialization (++) with daggers, short swords, scimitars, and long swords, and in Single-Weapon Style. May not gain proficiency with any two-handed weapons.
- May place 3 slots (+++) in Two-Weapon Style.
- Instead of singing, blades perform the Blade Dance. This impressive and complicated set of weapon maneuvers causes opponents to hesitate when attacking. The Blade receives a 2-point AC bonus and nearby enemies suffer from -2 thac0 and -1 damage penalties. At levels 13 and 20 these effects increase, and opponents must save vs. spells or become Panicked.
- May use the Defensive Spin ability once per day, and gains one use additional use for each every 4 levels of experience beyond first.

DEFENSIVE SPIN: During the next 4 rounds, the Blade is rooted to the spot and gains a +1 bonus to Armor Class per level, up to a maximum of +10.

Restrictions:
– Only has one half the normal Lore value.
– Only has one half the normal Pick Pockets skill.
~
